msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Window Title"
msgid "Copy DK Files"
msgstr "复制DK文件"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Header"
msgid "Copy Dungeon Keeper Files"
msgstr "复制地下城守护者文件"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Information"
msgid ""
"KeeperFX requires the original Dungeon Keeper files for copyright reasons.\n"
"Please select the directory where these files are located.\n"
"\n"
"You can use your original CD, or a digital version from GOG, Steam or EA.\n"
"If you want to use a digital version you will have to install it first."
msgstr ""
"由于版权原因，安装地下城守护者FX版需要提供原版游戏的文件。\n"
"请选择原版游戏文件的目录。\n"
"\n"
"你可以插入原版游戏CD，或导入GOG，Steam，EA等平台上的数字版游戏。\n"
"如果您想使用数字版游戏，请先将其安装。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Button"
msgid "Browse"
msgstr "浏览"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Button"
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "复制"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Label"
msgid "A suitable DK installation has been automatically detected."
msgstr "已自动检测到正确安装的地下城守护者游戏。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|Directory Browse Dialog"
msgid "Select Directory containing Dungeon Keeper files"
msgstr "请选择地下城守护者游戏文件目录"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Original DK files not found"
msgstr "未找到原版DK游戏文件"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"The chosen directory does not contain all of the required files. Please "
"select an original Dungeon Keeper installation."
msgstr "选择的目录缺少必需的文件。请选择原版地下城守护者游戏的安装目录。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Select a directory"
msgstr "选择目录"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Please select an original Dungeon Keeper installation location."
msgstr "请选择原版地下城守护者游戏的安装路径。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Failed to copy files"
msgstr "复制文件失败"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "The current directory is not writable."
msgstr "无法写入当前目录。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Something went wrong while copying the files."
msgstr "复制文件时出现错误。"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "DK files copied!"
msgstr "DK文件已复制！"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"The required Dungeon Keeper files have been copied.\n"
"\n"
"You can now play KeeperFX!"
msgstr ""
"所需的地下城守护者游戏文件已复制。\n"
"\n"
"你现在可以游玩FX版游戏了！"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "确认"

msgctxt "CopyDkFilesDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Are you sure?\n"
"\n"
"KeeperFX will not function correctly without these files."
msgstr ""
"你确定吗？\n"
"\n"
"缺少这些文件，FX版游戏可能无法正常运行。"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Window Title"
msgid "KeeperFX Crash Report"
msgstr "FX版游戏崩溃报告"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Header"
msgid "KeeperFX has crashed"
msgstr "FX版游戏崩溃了"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"It seems that KeeperFX has crashed and is unable to recover. If you wish to "
"submit technical details about this crash to the KeeperFX developers, you "
"can describe your problem below and click 'Send'. If you add contact details "
"we can contact you later. Additional information such as KeeperFX logfiles "
"and configuration will be sent too."
msgstr ""
"FX 版游戏似乎已崩溃且无法恢复。如果您想向 FX 版游戏开发人员提交有关此次崩溃的"
"技术细节，请在下方描述您的问题，然后点击“发送”。如果您添加联系方式，我们可以"
"稍后与您联系。其他信息（例如FX 版游戏日志文件和配置）也将一同发送。"

#, qt-format
msgctxt "CrashDialog|Information Label"
msgid "You can also raise an issue on Github: %1"
msgstr "您也可以在Github上提一个issue：%1"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input box title"
msgid "Information (Optional)"
msgstr "信息（可选）"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Textarea Placeholder"
msgid ""
"Please explain what happened, and if possible the steps to reproduce this "
"crash."
msgstr "请描述发生了什么，并尽可能逐步说明导致此次崩溃的操作。"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input box title"
msgid "Savefile (Optional)"
msgstr "保存文件（可选）"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Dropdown Placeholder Text"
msgid ""
"If you have a game save that could provide us with more information. You can "
"add it here."
msgstr "如果您有游戏存档，可以提供给我们更多信息。请在此处添加。"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input box title"
msgid "Contact Information (Optional)"
msgstr "联系方式（可选）"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input Placeholder"
msgid "Discord handle"
msgstr "Discord 账户"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input Placeholder"
msgid "KeeperFX.net username"
msgstr "KeeperFX.net 用户名"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Input Placeholder"
msgid "Email Address"
msgstr "电子邮箱"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Button"
msgid "Send"
msgstr "发送"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Menu Placeholder"
msgid "No saves found"
msgstr "未找到存档"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|Default Savefile"
msgid "None"
msgstr "无"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Crash Report"
msgstr "崩溃报告"

msgctxt "CrashDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Failed to submit crash report."
msgstr "提交崩溃报告失败。"

#, qt-format
msgctxt "CrashDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Your crash report has been successfully submitted!\n"
"\n"
"The KeeperFX team can not guarantee immediate results, but your feedback is "
"very helpful for the developers working on KeeperFX.\n"
"\n"
"Report ID: %1"
msgstr ""
"您的崩溃报告已成功提交！\n"
"\n"
"FX版游戏开发团队无法保证立即解决问题，但您的反馈对FX版游戏的开发者非常有帮"
"助。\n"
"\n"
"报告 ID：%1"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Window Title"
msgid "Direct Connect"
msgstr "直连"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Header"
msgid "Direct Connect"
msgstr "直连"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"Directly connect to an open ENET lobby. Enter the IP address of the host. "
"Only ENET is supported."
msgstr "直接连接到开放的 ENET 大厅。输入主机的 IP 地址。仅支持 ENET。"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Input Placeholder"
msgid "IP Address"
msgstr "IP地址"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Input Placeholder"
msgid "Port"
msgstr "端口"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|Button"
msgid "Connect"
msgstr "连接"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Direct Connect"
msgstr "直连"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Invalid IP address"
msgstr "无效的IP地址"

msgctxt "DirectConnectDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "IPv6 addresses are not supported."
msgstr "不支持IPv6地址。"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Dialog Title"
msgid "KeeperFX Background Music"
msgstr "FX版背景音乐"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Header"
msgid "Download Music Files"
msgstr "下载音乐文件"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Information"
msgid ""
"It seems the background music files were not found. This might happen when "
"you copied over the Dungeon Keeper files from the CD instead of a digital "
"release.\n"
"\n"
"You can let the launcher automatically download them because you have "
"already proven your ownership of the original Dungeon Keeper game files.\n"
"\n"
"If you do not download the music files you will need to have the original CD "
"in your disk drive to hear the background music."
msgstr ""
"似乎找不到背景音乐文件。这可能是因为您从 游戏CD 而不是数字版游戏复制了地下城"
"守护者文件。\n"
"\n"
"您可以使用启动器自动下载这些文件，因为您已经证明了自己拥有原版地下城守护者游"
"戏文件的所有权。\n"
"\n"
"如果您没有下载音乐文件，则需要将原版 CD 放入磁盘驱动器才能收听背景音乐。"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Button"
msgid "Download"
msgstr "下载"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Failed to get download URL for music archive"
msgstr "获取音乐文档的下载URL失败"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Invalid music archive file extension. It must be a 7zip archive."
msgstr "无效的音乐文档文件扩展包。必须是7zip格式的。"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Failed to download music archive"
msgstr "下载音乐文档失败"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Failure message"
msgid "Music archive test failed. It may be corrupted."
msgstr "音乐文档测试失败。它可能已损坏。"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Progress bar"
msgid "Extracting: %p%"
msgstr "提取中： %p%"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "The KeeperFX background music has been successfully downloaded!"
msgstr "FX版背景音乐已成功下载！"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|Progress bar"
msgid "Downloading: %p% (%vMiB)"
msgstr "下载中: %p% (%vMiB)"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Download failed"
msgstr "下载失败"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "确认"

msgctxt "DownloadMusicDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Are you sure?\n"
"\n"
"You will not be able to hear the background music without having your CD in "
"your disk drive."
msgstr ""
"你确定吗？\n"
"\n"
"如果你的光驱内未插入CD，你将无法听到游戏背景音乐。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Window Title"
msgid "Test internet lobby"
msgstr "测试网络大厅"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Header"
msgid "Multiplayer Lobby Portforwarding Test"
msgstr "多人游戏大厅端口转发测试"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"This tool checks if your KeeperFX multiplayer lobby can be reached from the "
"internet. You don't need to use this for local games, as those are already "
"accessible within your network."
msgstr ""
"此工具用于检查您的FX版多人游戏大厅是否可以通过互联网访问。本地游戏无需使用此"
"工具，因为本地游戏在您的网络中已经可以访问。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"To host a game online, you must open port 5556 in your router. How to do "
"this is different for every router and internet provider, so check online "
"for instructions or ask your provider for help."
msgstr ""
"要开始在线游戏，您必须在路由器上打开 5556 端口。每个路由器和互联网提供商的操"
"作方法都不同，因此请在线查看相关说明或向您的提供商寻求帮助。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"KeeperFX only works with IPv4. If you don't have an IPv4 address or you are "
"using a shared one (CGNAT), you won't be able to host an online game. You "
"can ask your internet provider if they can give you an IPv4 address."
msgstr ""
"FX 版游戏仅适用于 IPv4。如果您没有 IPv4 地址或正在使用共享地址 (CGNAT)，则无"
"法开始在线游戏。您可以咨询您的互联网服务提供商，他们是否可以为您提供 IPv4 地"
"址。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Button"
msgid "Close"
msgstr "关闭"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|Button"
msgid "Test"
msgstr "测试"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "IPv6 Detected"
msgstr "检测到IPv6"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Failed to retrieve public IP address."
msgstr "检索公共IP地址失败。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "This tool only works with IPv4."
msgstr "此工具仅适用于IPv4。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Portforwarding tool"
msgstr "端口转发工具"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Failed to start ENET server."
msgstr "启动ENET服务器失败。"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Failed to contact KeeperFX.net"
msgstr "无法连接到 KeeperFX.net"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Your router is correctly port forwarded!"
msgstr "您的路由器端口转发正常！"

msgctxt "EnetServerTestDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Failed to connect to local ENET server."
msgstr "无法连接到本地ENET服务器。"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Window Title"
msgid "Remove leftover files"
msgstr "移除残留的文件"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Header"
msgid "Remove leftover files"
msgstr "移除残留的文件"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"The KeeperFX launcher has found files that were left over after KeeperFX was "
"updated. These files might cause issues and should be removed."
msgstr ""
"FX版游戏启动器检测到FX版游戏更新后遗留的文件。这些文件可能会引发问题，请将其"
"删除。"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Checkbox Toggle"
msgid "Always remove leftover files automatically"
msgstr "始终自动删除残留文件"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|Button"
msgid "Remove All"
msgstr "全部移除"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "确认"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"KeeperFX might not function correctly if these files are present.\n"
"\n"
"Are you sure you want to keep them?"
msgstr ""
"如果保留这些文件，可能导致FX版游戏无法正常运行。\n"
"\n"
"您确定要保留它们吗？"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Something went wrong while removing leftover files."
msgstr "删除残留文件时出现错误。"

msgctxt "FileRemoverDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid "Leftover files have been removed!"
msgstr "残留文件已成功删除！"

msgctxt "Game|MessageBox Title"
msgid "KeeperFX has crashed"
msgstr "FX版游戏崩溃了"

msgctxt "Game|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"It seems that KeeperFX has crashed and is unable to recover.\n"
"\n"
"Crash reporting is disabled because you are using the heavylog option.\n"
"\n"
"If you require assistance, please create an issue on Github or contact us on "
"the Keeper Klan Discord."
msgstr ""
"FX版游戏似乎已崩溃且无法恢复。\n"
"\n"
"由于您使用了 heavylog 选项，崩溃报告功能已被禁用。\n"
"\n"
"如果您需要帮助，请在GitHub网站提交 issue或通过Keeper Klan Discord社群联系我"
"们。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Window Title"
msgid "Install KeeperFX"
msgstr "安装地下城守护者FX版"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Header"
msgid "Download and Install KeeperFX"
msgstr "下载并安装地下城守护者FX版"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Information Label"
msgid ""
"Select your version, and this installer will download and install KeeperFX.\n"
"\n"
"Choose the stable release for reliability or the alpha version if you want "
"to help us out with testing."
msgstr ""
"选择您的游戏版本，安装程序将下载并安装对应的FX版游戏。\n"
"\n"
"为了确保稳定性，请选择已发布的正式版本；如果您想帮助我们进行测试，请选择Alpha"
"测试版本。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Label"
msgid "Release version:"
msgstr "已发布版本："

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Button"
msgid "Install"
msgstr "安装"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Game Release Build"
msgid "Stable (Default)"
msgstr "稳定（默认）"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Game Release Build"
msgid "Alpha"
msgstr "Alpha"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Failed to get download URL for stable release"
msgstr "获取正式版本的下载URL链接失败"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Failed to download stable release"
msgstr "下载正式版本失败"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure message"
msgid "Stable release archive test failed. It may be corrupted."
msgstr "正式版本文档测试失败。它可能已损坏。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Progress bar"
msgid "Extracting: %p%"
msgstr "提取中： %p%"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure message"
msgid "Failed to create temp directory"
msgstr "创建临时目录失败"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure message"
msgid "Failed to get download URL for alpha patch"
msgstr "获取 Alpha 补丁的下载URL链接失败"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure message"
msgid "Alpha patch download failed."
msgstr "Alpha 补丁下载失败。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Failure Message"
msgid "Alpha patch archive test failed. It may be corrupted."
msgstr "Alpha补丁文档测试失败。它可能已损坏。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Progress bar"
msgid "Downloading: %p% (%vMiB)"
msgstr "下载中: %p% (%vMiB)"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Installation failed"
msgstr "安装失败"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "KeeperFX Alpha builds"
msgstr "FX版游戏Alpha补丁"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Alpha patches may contain new features and changes, but often contain bugs "
"and unfinished functionality. These patches are mostly meant for testers, "
"and it is suggested to be part of the Keeper Klan discord if you use them.\n"
"\n"
"Are you sure you want to use Alpha patches?"
msgstr ""
"Alpha 补丁可能包含新内容和更改，但很可能包含bug和未完善的内容。这些补丁主要面"
"向测试人员，如果您打算使用它们，建议您加入 Keeper Klan Discord社区。\n"
"\n"
"您确定要使用 Alpha 补丁吗？"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Uninstall KeeperFX"
msgstr "卸载FX版游戏"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Do you want to uninstall KeeperFX?\n"
"\n"
"This will remove any leftover files."
msgstr ""
"你确定要卸载FX版游戏吗？\n"
"\n"
"这将删除所有剩余的文件。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Title"
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "确认"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|MessageBox Text"
msgid ""
"Are you sure?\n"
"\n"
"You will be unable to play KeeperFX."
msgstr ""
"你确定吗？\n"
"\n"
"你将无法游玩FX版游戏。"

msgctxt "InstallKfxDialog|Progress bar"
msgid "Copying: %p%"
msgstr "复制中: %p%"

